rows.label: qst201406_msg0001
rows.name: What are you two doing, mo?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0002
rows.name: Hana, you came at the perfect time.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm having a Girl Power
competition with Zakuro, and
I'd like you to be the judge.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0004
rows.name:
Understood, mo! Leave that
mission to Hana, mo!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0005
rows.name:
Hana will give a fair judgment,
so we can rest easy!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0006
rows.name: Let's talk about crushes!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0007
rows.name:
This is the classic
topic for girls' talk!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0008
rows.name:
You really like talking
about crushes, Zakuro...
Not that I dislike it.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0009
rows.name:
Are you interested in that
sort of thing, Hana?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm curious about that
too! How about it, Hana?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0011
rows.name:
Crushes... Is that a new
type of flower, mo?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0012
rows.name: No, no! Not flowers, love!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0013
rows.name: Is there anyone you like, Hana?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0014
rows.name: Hana loves everyone, mo!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0015
rows.name: Hmm... That's not what I meant...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0016
rows.name:
In any case, to judge Girl Power,
why not use housekeeping skills
instead of crushes, mo?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0017
rows.name:
As a maid, cleaning, laundry, and
cooking are all easy for Hana, mo!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0018
rows.name:
Hana is confident that she is far
superior to Hikari and Zakuro, mo.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0019
rows.name: W-Well, that's certainly...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0020
rows.name:
I'm just a little bad at
cooking, that's all...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0021
rows.name:
Therefore, Hana declares herself
the winner, mo! Hmph, mo!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0022
rows.name: I'm not quite convinced by that...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0023
rows.name: We can't beat Hana at housekeeping.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0024
rows.name: This one's a draw...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0025
rows.name: I suppose so...
